metadata.name: 𝐈'𝐦 𝐒𝐭𝐢𝐥𝐥 𝐅𝐢𝐠𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐌𝐲𝐬𝐞𝐥𝐟 𝐎𝐮𝐭
metadata.description:
Sometimes my mind feels like a maze with no way out,  
I'm learning how to not be so hard on myself..  
With anxiety that could swallow me whole,  
I'm learning to accept the harsher parts of my soul.  
In this body that carries me everyday,  
I'm still trying to find my way.
